WEBVTT

1
00:03:35.720 --> 00:03:37.050 
你怎么跑到我手机里的
How'd you get in my phone?

2
00:03:37.500 --> 00:03:39.250 
这是不是意味着那天我们通话时
Does this mean when we talked the other day

3
00:03:39.250 --> 00:03:40.750 
你知道我是在厕所里
that you knew I was in the can?

4
00:03:40.750 --> 00:03:41.430 
我这下知道了
I do now.

5
00:03:41.430 --> 00:03:42.650 
会议展示做得怎么样
How was the presentation?

6
00:03:42.650 --> 00:03:43.580 
非常顺利
Actually went really well.

7
00:03:43.580 --> 00:03:45.120 
客户喜欢我们的新设计
The client loves the whole re-design.

8
00:03:45.120 --> 00:03:46.390 
但希望我们换掉长方形把手
They just want us to swap out the handles --

9
00:03:46.390 --> 00:03:48.000 
-该死的  -我懂的
- Damn it! - I know.

10
00:03:48.000 --> 00:03:49.730 
只有蠢货才会想要旋钮
Only knobs want knobs.

11
00:03:49.730 --> 00:03:52.660 
不是  是乔咬了我  他在出牙
No, Joe bit me. He's teething.

12
00:03:52.660 --> 00:03:53.950 
我觉得安迪这周末请假
I don't think it's a coincidence

13
00:03:53.950 --> 00:03:55.610 
不是巧合
that Andy took the weekend off.

14
00:03:56.310 --> 00:03:57.630 
这孩子跟海狸似的
Kid's like a beaver.

15
00:03:57.630 --> 00:03:59.180 
我都不敢穿短裤了
I'm afraid to wear short pants.

16
00:03:59.180 --> 00:04:00.800 
好啊  克莱尔
Hola, Claire.

17
00:04:00.800 --> 00:04:01.590 
好啊  歌洛莉亚
Hey, Gloria.

18
00:04:01.600 --> 00:04:03.900 
出差怎么样  玩得开心吗
How's your trip? Are you having any fun?

19
00:04:03.910 --> 00:04:08.100 
是啊  风有点大  但是
Uh...yeah. You know, it's a little windy, but, eh.

